â€˜@titlepageâ€™ and â€˜@end titlepageâ€™ commands:

     @titlepage
     @title Sample Title

     @c The following two commands start the copyright page.
     @page
     @vskip 0pt plus 1filll
     @insertcopying
     @end titlepage

We use the â€˜@insertcopyingâ€™ command to include the permission text from
the previous section, instead of writing it out again.

