3.9.1 Writing a Menu
--------------------

A menu consists of a â€˜@menuâ€™ command on a line by itself, followed by
menu entry lines or menu comment lines, and then followed by an â€˜@end
menuâ€™ command on a line by itself.

   A menu looks like this:

     @menu
