     * Files::                       All about handling files.
     * Multiples: Buffers.           Multiple buffers; editing
                                      several files at once.
     @end menu

   In a menu, every line that begins with an â€˜* â€™ is a â€œmenu entryâ€.
(Note the space after the asterisk.)

   A line that does not start with an â€˜* â€™ may also appear in a menu.
Such a line is not a menu entry but rather a â€œmenu commentâ€ line that
appears in the Info file.  In the example above, the line â€˜Larger Units
of Textâ€™ is such a menu comment line; the two lines starting with â€˜* â€™
are menu entries.

