4.5 â€˜@majorheadingâ€™, â€˜@chapheadingâ€™: Chapter-level Headings
===========================================================

The â€˜@majorheadingâ€™ and â€˜@chapheadingâ€™ commands produce chapter-like
headings in the body of a document.

