whitespace before the heading than a â€˜@chapheadingâ€™ command but is
otherwise the same.

   In other output formats, the â€˜@majorheadingâ€™ and â€˜@chapheadingâ€™
commands produce a similar output to â€˜@chapterâ€™.  The difference is the
lack of numbering and the lack of any association with nodes.  *Note*
@chapter::.


