4.6 â€˜@sectionâ€™: Sections Below Chapters
=======================================

An â€˜@sectionâ€™ command identifies a section within a chapter unit,
whether created with â€˜@chapterâ€™, â€˜@unnumberedâ€™, or â€˜@appendixâ€™,
following the numbering scheme of the chapter-level command.  Thus,
