commands are written on lines of their own, without braces.  The
â€˜@flushleftâ€™ and â€˜@flushrightâ€™ commands are ended by â€˜@end flushleftâ€™
and â€˜@end flushrightâ€™ commands on lines of their own.

   For example,

     @flushleft
