7.13 â€˜@indentâ€™: Forcing Indentation
===================================

   To complement the â€˜@noindentâ€™ command (see the previous section),
Texinfo provides the â€˜@indentâ€™ command to force a paragraph to be
indented.  For instance, this paragraph (the first in this section) is
indented using an â€˜@indentâ€™ command.

   And indeed, the first paragraph of a section is the most likely place
to use â€˜@indentâ€™, to override the normal behavior of no indentation
