===============================

In addition to the regular â€˜@exampleâ€™ and similar commands, Texinfo has
"small" example-style commands.  These are â€˜@smallquotationâ€™,
â€˜@smallindentedblockâ€™, â€˜@smalldisplayâ€™, â€˜@smallexampleâ€™, â€˜@smallformatâ€™,
