12.2 â€˜@*â€™ and â€˜@/â€™: Generate and Allow Line Breaks
==================================================

The â€˜@*â€™ command forces a line break in all output formats.  The â€˜@/â€™
command allows a line break (printed manual only).

   Here is an example with â€˜@*â€™:

