14.1 â€˜@documentlanguage LL[_CC]â€™: Set the Document Language
===========================================================

The â€˜@documentlanguageâ€™ command declares the current document locale.
Write it on a line by itself, near the beginning of the file.

     @documentlanguage LL[_CC]

