15.3 Raw Formatter Commands
===========================

The â€˜@if...â€™ conditionals just described must be used only with normal
Texinfo source.  For instance, most features of plain TeX will not work
within â€˜@iftexâ€™.  The purpose of â€˜@if...â€™ is to provide conditional
processing for Texinfo source, not provide access to underlying
formatting features.  For that, Texinfo provides so-called â€œraw
formatter commandsâ€.  They should only be used when truly required (most
documents do not need them).

