longer the case.  For example:

     @macro twolines{}
     aaa
     bbb
     @end macro
     @center @twolines{}

   In the current â€˜texi2anyâ€™, this is equivalent to:

     @center aaa
     bbb

with just â€˜aaaâ€™ as the argument to â€˜@centerâ€™.  In the earlier
implementation, it would have been parsed as this:

     @center aaa bbb


