16.6 â€˜@definfoencloseâ€™: Customized Highlighting
===============================================

An â€˜@definfoencloseâ€™ command may be used to define a highlighting
command for online output formats.  A command defined using
â€˜@definfoencloseâ€™ marks text by enclosing it in strings that precede and
