â€˜--no-validateâ€™ option (*note* Invoking texi2any::).

   Furthermore, you need not run â€˜texindexâ€™ each time after you run
â€˜texâ€™.  The â€˜texâ€™ formatting command simply uses whatever sorted index
files happen to exist from a previous use of â€˜texindexâ€™.  If those are
out of date, that is usually ok while you are creating or debugging a
document.


