(â€˜forward-pageâ€™) and â€˜C-x [â€™ (â€˜backward-pageâ€™) commands and narrow to a
chapter with the â€˜C-x n pâ€™ (â€˜narrow-to-pageâ€™) command.  (*Note*
(emacs)Pages::, for details about the page commands.)

