     commands will reflect the situation at the bottom of a page).
     These â€˜@every...â€™ commands specify what to do on both even- and
     odd-numbered pages.

â€˜@evenheadingmarks REFâ€™
â€˜@oddheadingmarks REFâ€™
â€˜@evenfootingmarks REFâ€™
â€˜@oddfootingmarks REFâ€™
     These â€˜@even...â€™ and â€˜@odd...â€™ commands specify what to do on only
