F.5 Info Format: Local Variables
================================

The local variables section is optional and is currently used to give
the encoding information.  It may be augmented in the future.

         <local variables> =
     <separator>
     Local Variables:
     coding: <encoding>
     End:

   *Note* @documentencoding::.


